msgid "Security updates"
msgstr ""

#: ../../_doc/user/how-to-guides/how-to-update.md:18
#: f81652674fd1459d99cef4d279146158
msgid ""
"Security updates are an extremely important part of keeping your Qubes "
"installation secure. When there is an important security issue, we will "
"issue a [Qubes Security Bulletin (QSB)](/security/qsb/) via the [Qubes "
"Security Pack (`qubes-secpack`)](/security/pack/). It is very important to "
"read each new QSB and follow any user instructions it contains. Most of the "
"time, simply [updating your system normally](#routine-updates) will be "
"sufficient to obtain security updates. However, in some cases, special "
"action may be required on your part, which will be explained in the QSB."
msgstr ""

